                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.00/8027: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">Then in France</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-09-08T12:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 8, 1936—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>B–19. Your 96, September 7, 4 p.m. We do not desire you to associate yourself
                    with any joint representations or joint appeal on this subject.</p>
                <p>For your strictly confidential information, we are assembling the facts with the
                    view if deemed justifiable of giving consideration to an independent appeal to
                    both factions against the use of gas against towns and cities, or alternatively
                    to a statement to the press expressing our views on this subject. We will keep
                    you informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
